subject: ATTENTION: DEAR BENEFICIARY,
body:

GOOD MORNING, I AM MR ALFRED SCHIPKE IMF SENIOR RESIDENT REPRESENTATIVE UNITED STATE OF AMERICA,I USE THIS OPPORTUNITY TO GET IN CONTACT WITH YOU REGARDING YOUR $3.7 MILLION UNITED STATE DOLLARS IN OUR CUSTODY. YOURS FAITHFULLY,
ALFRED SCHIPKE,

subject: Re:   ATTENTION: DEAR BENEFICIARY,
body:
Hello Mr. Alfred Schipke,

Good morning! I hope this message finds you well. It's quite surprising to hear about the million dollars in your custody that you mentioned. Could you please provide more details about this? How did it come into your possession and why is it meant for me?

I'm looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Blair
